reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent quality,fast charging,low price,perfect!!!
reviews.reviewText: This 20W USB C Fast Charger with 10FT Lightning Cable has exceeded my expectations in every way possible.This charger kit is an absolute game-changer for any iPhone user who values both speed and rliability.The appearance of this charger is beautiful and eye-catching,it is different from other chargers,and it is very clever and simple.I like it.The bulid quality of the charger and cables is outstanding.Both the adapter and the cables are made of durable materials that feel sturdy and well-constructed.I appreciate the attention to detail,as they not only function flawlessly but also withstand the rigors of everyday use.The compact and lightweight design of the adapter makes it highly portable,making it a perfect travel companion.The charging speed is simply phenomenal.With the 20W power delivery,this charger provides lightning-fast charging for my phone.Gone are the days of endlessly waiting for my device to charge up.It efficiently charges my phone battery to full capacity in no time,allowing me to stay connected and productive throughout the day.In conclsion,the iPhone Charger Fast Charging Kit with apple MFI certification is a dependable and efficient charging solution for your apple devices.It offers fast charging,an extra-long cable,and the assurance of apple's quality and safety standards.The two pack provides added value for households with multiple devices.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for money fast charging chargers
reviews.reviewText: This charger has a 20W power output and provides lightning fast charging for my iPhone,charging my iPhone 14 from 8% to 68% in about 30-45 minutes.It's perfect for when I am in a hurry and keeps me productive throughout the day.The quality of the charger's adapter and cable is excellent and looks very sturdy and well-made,both made from durable,hight-quality materials.The 2 pack is so convenient,one I keep in my bedroomand the other in my bag for charging on the go .And the cable length is amazing.10ft is long enough that I can comfortably charge my iPhone even if the wall outlet is a little far away,which I realy like.This charger set is definitely a great value for money and can also be used for home use.It is highly recommended to buy it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cheap fast charging
reviews.reviewText: The 2 chargers work perfectly! The fast charging works as it should and the price is really hard to beat for 2 chargers with long cords. The 10 foot cords are honestly game changers!The chargers seem pretty durable so far, but only time will tell. Especially considering the price, the chargers are worth it to me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These work well for a little bit, but end up not working. They are not fast charging at all. If you need a long cord and don’t care about charging speed, these will do the trick for a few months.

One friend had a this brand speed charger,so I immediately came on here and order some.They work so great and my iphone charges extremely fast.I do not even have the words to describe how fast these charge.I am a chaotic person who will forget to charge their iphone at sensible times,so I really need to have several chargers,one in my house,one at my work,etc.These are awesome and juice up my iphone 13 in under 30 minutes for a fully dead battery.Even a short 10 minute charge takes my iphone from a dead battery to useable.As of now, I can say that I am absolutely satisfied with the purchase.High recommended!
